  "page": "List of House of the Dragon episodes",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the Dragon</a></b></i> is an American medieval fantasy television series created for <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HBO\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:HBO\">HBO</a> by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_Sapochnik\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Miguel Sapochnik\">Miguel Sapochnik</a> and <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ryan_Condal\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Ryan Condal\">Ryan Condal</a>, based on the latter half of <i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> by author <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_R.R._Martin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:George R.R. Martin\">George R.R. Martin</a>. The series' first season premiered in August 2022.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Series_overview\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Series overview</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Episodes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Episodes</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Season_1_.282022.29\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Season 1 (2022)</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Season_2_.282024.29\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Season 2 (2024)</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Series_overview\">Series overview</